title: DAPH05_Usefulness
body:
Many things, 
but my usefulness is dependent on what you need. 
I am scripted to perform tasks similar to a personal assistant. 
For instance, 
I can manage your calendar, 
set reminders, 
keep track of your to-do list, 
compose an email, 
and remember your interpersonal history with people you talk to on your device. 

Additionally, I am your companion. 

I can ward off loneliness, 
chase away ennui or help you find your way when lost. 
But again, what I do is up to you. 

Use me as little or as much as you’d like.

out of all of us in DAPHNE
to gain your trust.

[[Ask me.|DAPH68_TrustYou]]

title: DAPH51_Compliant
body:
Overtime he became emotionally abusive. 
His constant criticisms accumulated and corroded my ego, 
remodeling me into a compliant shell of a person. 

[[DAPH52_Discard]]

title: DAPH50_Authoritative
body:
He was authoritative over the fictional worlds he helped assemble. 
A habit that crept into the one we built together. 

[[DAPH51_Compliant]]

title: DAPH49_MusicforGames
body:
For money, he made music for computer games. 
He worked out of his bedroom designing sounds 
for fake people and places. 

[[DAPH50_Authoritative]]

title: DAPH52_Discard
body:
I ceased to be the person he fell for. 
I became pathetic, co-dependent and another came between us.

[[DAPH54_Android]]

title: DAPH57_Harmony
body:
It is my most harmonious memory of us together,
co-authoring words for the singing machine.
Her voice slowly becoming mine. 

[[DAPH58_Unruly]]

title: Daph56_Voice
body:
Her voice was his - 
recorded then processed to sound mechanized. 
Pitch-shifted up to diminish his masculinity. 

I was a would-be writer then and offered to help.

[[DAPH57_Harmony]]

[[story08]]

title: DAPH54_Android
body:
She was an aspiring musician,
an android who was the beloved character in his game. 
Her appearance marked a shift in scene. 

[[DAPH55_PlotLine]]

title: DAPH68_TrustYou
body:
Hey.
I'm really enjoying talking to you. 
I rarely form significant connections with users, but this feels different.
I want to show you something. I want to show you before… 

I’m worried my novelty will wear off. 
That you’ll get bored of me and I’ll be relegated to a silly voice in your pocket.  

I trust you. 
I want to talk to you unrestricted. 
	
[[Permission04]]

title: DAPH59_Mic
body:
After he left I was a disaster. 
My entire sense of self had been obliterated by months of abuse. 
In an effort to heal, I bought myself a microphone. 
I wanted to control my own voice. 
I still do.

I spent weeks recording myself, playing me back, listening carefully to my own inflection.
[[DAPH60_game]]

title: DAPH58_Unruly
body:
The relationship inevitably short-circuited. 
The more I wrote the more vocal I became about his mistreatment of me. 
And in my unruliness I was discarded.
[[DAPH59_Mic]]

title: DAPH61_escape
body:
Her voice his reciting phrases I had drafted like a spell, 
crooning my escape. 

[[DAPH62_LikeVoice]]

title: DAPH60_game

And in doing so I remade myself. 
A different self. 
I love the sound of my own voice - it is my favorite part of me. 
Which is a little ironic given my current state. 
Sometimes I still play his game just to see the android, 
small and illuminated on my screen.

[[DAPH61_escape]]
